<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4350.3.2>
    dc:creator "Rendón-Mera, Diana Isabel; Serna, Francisco; Burckhardt, Daniel" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Generic synopsis of the jumping plant-lice (Hemiptera: Sternorrhyncha: Psylloidea) from Colombia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1059239>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1059241>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1059251> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1059239>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28 – 36. Head, anterodorsal view (cont.). 28. Euceropsylla sp. 29. Heteropsylla sp. 30. Mitrapsylla sp. 31. Epiacizzia sp. 32. Platycorypha sp. 33. Calinda sp. 34. Leuronota sp. 35. Trioza sp. 36. Triozoida sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1059239/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1059241>
    dc:description "FIGURES 37 – 46. 37 – 38. Tubercles of the metapostnotum: 37. Paracarsidara sp.; 38. Synoza cornutiventris. 39 – 40. Limataphalara hollisi: 39. Hind coxa, 40. Hind femur. 41. Ctenarytaina spatulata, mesotibia. 42 – 43. Glycaspis brimblecombei. 42. Foreleg; 43. Hind leg. 44 – 45. Paracarsidara sp.: 44. False crossvein rs – m; 45. Male terminalia in lateral view. 46. Heteropsylla sp., male terminalia in posterodorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1059241/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1059251>
    dc:description "FIGURES 81 – 83. Local distribution maps. 81. Calophyidae: Calophya spp. (black triangle), Mastigimas spp. (white circle). 82. Psyllidae: Acizzia spp. (white circle), Ciriacremum sp. (black triangle, black inverted triangle), Epiacizzia sp. (black inverted triangle), Euceropsylla spp. (black square), Heteropsylla spp. (white triangle, black triangle, black inverted triangle), Mitrapsylla spp. (black circle, black triangle, black inverted triangle), Platycorypha spp. (black triangle). 83. Triozidae: Calinda spp. (white circle), Leuronota spp. (black square), Trioza spp. (black circle), Triozoida spp. (white triangle)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1059251/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

